              <div style="width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:14px;background:rgba(34,197,94,.15);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,.3);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:34px;flex-shrink:0;">📷</div>
              <div>
                <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:900;font-size:28px;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--success);">CCTV &amp; Security</h2>
                <p style="color:var(--gray-light);line-height:1.75;max-width:520px;">Analog and IP camera installations, DVR/NVR setup, remote access configuration, electric fence installation, access control systems, and video intercom.</p>
