          <div class="trust-card"><div class="trust-icon">⚡</div><h3 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:8px;">Fast Response</h3><p style="color:var(--gray-light);font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;">Average dispatch under 60 minutes for standard jobs. Emergency requests handled within 30 minutes.</p></div>
